name: ⚡ Anh Tú Premium - Stash
desc: 67 Apps - Locket Gold + YouTube + Spotify + SoundCloud + PicsArt + Lightroom + Photoshop + Emby + KineMaster + Djay + Calm + Busuu + Headspace + AlightMotion + Wink + Truecaller + CamScanner + BeautyPlus + VSCO + Snow + B612 + Meitu + Funimate + iTunes + WPS + Xmind + Alarmy + Grammarly + Notability + Photomath + Smallpdf + Peak + Polarr + MyFitnessPal + Musixmatch + Fimo + Varlens + Darkroom + OldRoll + PhotoRoom + Pixelcut + Mojo + Boom + Audiomack + Fantastical + Craft + DayOne + Nicegram + iLovePDF + Mondly + Memrise + Aloha + DailyYoga + AccuWeather + SparkMail + Endel + Flomo + Drafts + Keep + ColorWidgets + WidgetSmith + InVideo + Pandora + Beelinguapp + Relens + TouchRetouch + Emote + Sub-Store | v1.2.0 (2026-05-24)
author: Nguyễn Ngọc Anh Tú
homepage: https://github.com/ekaznyra/NguyenNgocAnhTu
icon: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Koolson/Qure/master/IconSet/Color/Apple.png

rules:
  # === BLOCK QUIC FOR YOUTUBE MITM ===
  # STASH NOT SUPPORT AND: AND,((DOMAIN-SUFFIX,googlevideo.com), (PROTOCOL,UDP)),REJECT
  # STASH NOT SUPPORT AND: AND,((DOMAIN,youtubei.googleapis.com), (PROTOCOL,UDP)),REJECT
  # === BLOCK WEBRTC LEAK ===
  - DOMAIN-KEYWORD,stun,REJECT
  - DOMAIN-KEYWORD,turn,REJECT
  # === SPOTIFY ADS ===
  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,audio-ak-spotify-com.akamaized.net,REJECT
  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,audio4-ak-spotify-com.akamaized.net,REJECT
  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,heads-ak-spotify-com.akamaized.net,REJECT
  - DOMAIN-SUFFIX,heads4-ak-spotify-com.akamaized.net,REJECT
  - DOMAIN,spclient.wg.spotify.com,DIRECT
  - DOMAIN-KEYWORD,spotify-ads,REJECT
